Class BaseFeatureGeometry

All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:
BasePolygon, BasePolyline
public abstract class BaseFeatureGeometry
extends BaseGeometry
implements FeatureGeometry

This class is the base implementation for FeatureGeometry. It provides partial support for java.awt.Shape by implementing most of the required methods. Sub-classes need to provide the getPathIteratorXXX methods.
